article.description: — Will Pruitt's 30 points led Lipscomb over Austin Peay 90-85 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Pruitt's 30 lead Lipscomb past Austin Peay 90-85
article.linkText: Pruitt's 30 lead Lipscomb past Austin Peay 90-85
article.story: CLARKSVILLE, Tenn. -- — Will Pruitt's 30 points led Lipscomb over Austin Peay 90-85 on Saturday night. Pruitt shot 13 for 16, including 4 for 5 from beyond the arc for the Bisons (18-11, 9-5 Atlantic Sun Conference). Cody Head scored 21 points while going 8 of 11 (3 for 5 from 3-point range). A.J McGinnis finished with 14 points. Dezi Jones finished with 30 points, four assists and two steals for the Governors (15-14, 8-6). Sai Witt added 23 points for Austin Peay. Isaac Haney also put up 16 points. The loss broke the Governors' five-game winning streak. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
